{"tid":189433,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底佢係我眼中有幾完美","createTime":"2017-04-06T12:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:20:38.000Z","uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"660931a56cadbc94f58ee9532760390dc2eb272c","tid":189433,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"完美到就算已經拒絕左我<br />\n都仲咁鐘意佢 每次諗起佢就傻笑 好開心<br />\n知道自己要move on 但係就係忘記唔到<br />\n佢對我做既野講既野 就算好小事 都記左好耐 記左係心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地仲要係同一個圈子 冇其他人知 但我真係好難受 好唔開心 已經忍左手 唔再搵佢<br />\n但係同圈子朋友口中知道佢既野 睇到佢既相 又會諗好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求屌醒 想放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bec2d5da0dc8c077b9fc81ef0fb0c70b26d3d50","tid":189433,"uid":82346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"迷戀閉眼才給美化"},{"pid":"8720b6cf49535a6831eeb728b2b6f8296d5aa678","tid":189433,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人拒絕咗 佢幾完美都唔關你事啦"},{"pid":"01b9335ae2618dbeb2dbe71d0ebc378e4b9cd1c2","tid":189433,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人拒絕咗 佢幾完美都唔關你事啦</blockquote><br />\n大力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主就係想畀人屌醒"},{"pid":"606c9dfd3474818426735b201abd3ae3f1bb6f08","tid":189433,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"你都係閪痕姐"},{"pid":"06a6794f1587009909dc7d6043bb515ab85571e3","tid":189433,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal